## DB 자주 쓰는 쿼리

```sql
-- 최신 daily_summary 확인
SELECT * FROM daily_summary ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 5;

-- 현재 tickers 시세 확인
SELECT ticker, name, current_price, change_pct, updated_at FROM tickers ORDER BY market, ticker;

-- positions 확인
SELECT p.id, a.name, p.ticker, p.quantity FROM positions p JOIN accounts a ON p.account_id = a.id;

-- NDX100 현재가
SELECT ticker, current_price, updated_at FROM tickers WHERE ticker = '^NDX';

-- USD/KRW 현재가
SELECT ticker, current_price, updated_at FROM tickers WHERE ticker = 'USDKRW=X';
```

